## Anti-patterns — DO NOT generate seeds for

- Causation claims — the pipeline reports correlations only, labeled as such.
- Sentiment analysis via model inference — keyword rules only.
- Queries joining >3 units/collections — use denormalized view operations instead.
- Fields listed in `config.yaml :: source.forbidden_fields` in filter/group/sort positions.
- Questions requiring >10K units loaded into Claude context — aggregate on the adapter side.
